<sect1 id="group__container__module_1container_overview">
<title>Overview</title>
<para>The Container module provides data container classes for efficient storage and management of analysis data, including graphs and tensors.</para>
</sect1>
<sect1 id="group__container__module_1container_features">
<title>Features</title>
<para><itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>Efficient memory management</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Serialization support (HDF5)</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Batch operations</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Device transfer (CPU/CUDA)</para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
<para><simplesect kind="see"><para><ref refid="classcontainer" kindref="compound">container</ref> </para>
</simplesect>
</para>
